		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Solar water disinfection</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Indonesia-sodis-gross.jpg" class="image" title="SODIS application in Indonesia"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/67/Indonesia-sodis-gross.jpg/180px-Indonesia-sodis-gross.jpg" width="180" height="135" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Indonesia-sodis-gross.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
SODIS application in <a href="/wiki/Indonesia" title="Indonesia">Indonesia</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<p><b>Solar water disinfection</b>, also known as <b>SODIS</b><sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> is a method of <a href="/wiki/Disinfection" title="Disinfection" class="mw-redirect">disinfecting</a> water using only <a href="/wiki/Sunlight" title="Sunlight">sunlight</a> and plastic <a href="/wiki/Polyethylene_terephthalate" title="Polyethylene terephthalate">PET</a> bottles. SODIS is a cheap and effective method for decentralized water treatment, usually applied at the household level and is recommended by the <a href="/wiki/World_Health_Organization" title="World Health Organization">World Health Organization</a> as a viable method for household water treatment and safe storage.<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1" title=""><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup> SODIS is already applied in numerous <a href="/wiki/Developing_countries" title="Developing countries" class="mw-redirect">developing countries</a>.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents">
