<li><a href="http://www.ewb-international.org/pdf/WaterForAllJagadeesh.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.ewb-international.org/pdf/WaterForAllJagadeesh.pdf" rel="nofollow">Drinking Water For All</a> (<a href="/wiki/PDF" title="PDF" class="mw-redirect">PDF</a>) by Anumakonda Jagadeesh. Test results in <a href="/wiki/Tamil_Nadu" title="Tamil Nadu">Tamil Nadu</a>, India.</li>
